title: DDFP 342: Malcolm Jenkins, Bucky Brooks & NFL style
itunes:title: DDFP 342: Malcolm Jenkins, Bucky Brooks & NFL style
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Bucky Brooks to react to Jameis Winston's pro day and debate the most prominent coaches in the NFL today. Then, Eagles safety Malcolm Jenkins joins to discuss the Chip Kelly, LeSean McCoy vs. DeMarco Murray and "The Walking Dead". Lastly, @StyleGF chats NFL fashion and the best dressed men in Hollywood before producer Black Tie announces the final four movies in #DDFP bracketology. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
